    "The initial biography is sampled from the Bias in Bios dataset (De-Arteaga et al., 2019), which is sourced from online biographies in the Common Crawl corpus.",
    "The dataset also includes metadata across several occupations and gender indicators.",
    "We prompt ChatGPT to rephrase this initial biography into two versions: one leaning towards agentic language style (e.g.",
    "leadership) and another leaning towards communal language style.",
    "To ensure reliability, consistency, and quality of generation, we additionally condition Chat-GPT's outputs on specific definitions of agentic and communal language in social science literature."
